item.title: CVE-2019-5223|2024-08-04T19:47:56.691Z -- huawei -- pc%20manager
item.description: PCManager 9.1.3.1 has an improper authentication vulnerability. The certain driver interface of the software does not perform a validation of user-mode data properly, successful exploit could result in malicious code execution.
